{"tid":1667630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發完夢之後發覺而家狗隻行緊兩種策略","createTime":"2019-10-21T14:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T15:20:56.000Z","uid":58841,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"292dbbf8a270f088b3cfc08a57559b8e0a9cff2f","tid":1667630,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"因為前線資訊非常混亂<br />\n郁啲就話有狗<br />\n其實好多時只係得一架狗車<br />\n甚至車上面淨係得司機<br />\n所以而家狗隻行緊車海戰術<br />\n令你地覺得好撚多兵<br />\n<br />\n解決方法：和理非同街坊要做哨<br />\n<br />\n第二就係狗隻唔敢行入內街/公園範圍內<br />\n好多時佢地只係stand by係大馬路<br />\n當我地成班人入左去內街/公園狗隻就無再追<br />\n我諗係狗隻怕落單<br />\n<br />\n解決方法：唔好沿大馬路行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">另外我其實想講好耐<br />\n前線係無必要殿後<br />\n我走到一半就發現我明明係和理非點解跑前面<br />\n於是我停低左一二邊做哨 班狗果然無追<br />\n<br />\n所以be water應該係：<br />\n狗&gt;街坊&gt;和理非&gt;前線&gt;和理非&gt;中排&gt;前線先岩<br />\n</span></span><br />\n所以請前線脫離保護和理非心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0501e3f1646f98d3cc66013af3d6f0fd70d5a0","tid":1667630,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:39:49.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"f4a43a8d9530db4c7c89a4ade531755e7391cf3f","tid":1667630,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:40:16.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"328b53d132c17817e0d5a27971048e6129e317f0","tid":1667630,"uid":138609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:40:23.000Z","msg":"住戰略要地既街坊和理非上晒天台<br />\n落街撚狗大把街坊會黎<br />\n住喺重要位置做哨更幫到大家"},{"pid":"738a3f2e553630edfa644f1e56c5b1cf4ae31c46","tid":1667630,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44276acc1bb353e709ec61ee423a1e0b7cb3045","tid":1667630,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"328b53d132c17817e0d5a27971048e6129e317f0","tid":1667630,"uid":138609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"c